short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Yiscogs inserts a Search on YouTube link after releaseses on Discogs to search YouTube for the release, without release format

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Yiscogs inserts a 'Search on YouTube' link after release titles on Discogs that searches YouTube for the release title, excluding the release format to ensure better search results, making it easier to listen to releases you are searching for. 
Specially handy while browsing through Marketplace collections. 
Enjoy!
